{"tid":345001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"時裝界之恥 MODEMENT","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T10:35:57.000Z","uid":133092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58da10752810c24c9c9356cf921d146bf3b7c227","tid":345001,"uid":133092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"我係一個設計師<br />\n諗返以前返實習公司 不得不提呢間垃圾<br />\n<br />\n全間公司一個正式員工都冇<br />\n每年期期都請幾個intern<br />\n但我地就仲衰過隻免費狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來都諗住學下野點知個伏就正式開始<br />\n------------------------------------------------------冇人工食飯包一餐算好好<br />\n但包一餐唔喺叫你出去買<br />\n係叫自己鐘點姨姨煮<br />\n你可能諗好健康 <br />\n但係結果晏晝都住埋比你<br />\n不過係晏晝夜晚食同一樣野<br />\n豆腐白菜魚湯加肉餅 分2餐10人分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫你去廠車衫改衫<br />\n由荔枝角去鑽石山 45分鐘問你去左邊到玩仲未返<br />\n係其他人面前瘋狂屌你慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期六返10點早上 <br />\n冇門口入 卡係腦西到<br />\n個老閪可以三點半先返<br />\n結果我地坐係地下門口5個鐘<br />\n當佢返到嚟講咗句嘩你地咁舒服坐係地下wtf<br />\n真心向左走向右走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從來自己坐房intern自己出面做<br />\n但每十幾分鐘出嚟屌下你<br />\n侮辱你冇腦 手腳慢 進度差 <br />\n話咁樣出黎做5000蚊都比多你地<br />\nWtf最低工資都唔只啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我地intern可以一日幫佢做18個鐘先肯放你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要唔只一日 係日日起碼工作12個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個腦閪去法國三個星期吃喝玩樂<br />\n交低做野 問又唔應機做完又唔滿意<br />\n可以話乜憑咩拎返屋企做<br />\n今日比你地做應該要今日完<br />\n個時11半夜晚 有人住離島<br />\n我地心諗冇撚野啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果做完唔滿意唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然仲有好多 不過一定比大家知呢間<br />\n本土時裝品牌<br />\n'偽善下三流'<br />\n'當學生係狗'<br />\n'冇料扮四條'<br />\n'孤寒用到盡'<br />\n'侮辱屌冇腦'<br />\n嘅時裝品牌 - MODEMENT"},{"pid":"bbb7f8d5c2f84d98de365b1fdc84d7e97bfe79e9","tid":345001,"uid":133092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係一個設計師<br />\n諗返以前返實習公司 不得不提呢間垃圾<br />\n<br />\n全間公司一個正式員工都冇<br />\n每年期期都請幾個intern<br />\n但我地就仲衰過隻免費狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來都諗住學下野點知個伏就正式開始<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------冇人工食飯包一餐算好好<br />\n但包一餐唔喺叫你出去買<br />\n係叫自己鐘點姨姨煮<br />\n你可能諗好健康 <br />\n但係結果晏晝都住埋比你<br />\n不過係晏晝夜晚食同一樣野<br />\n豆腐白菜魚湯加肉餅 分2餐10人分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫你去廠車衫改衫<br />\n由荔枝角去鑽石山 45分鐘問你去左邊到玩仲未返<br />\n係其他人面前瘋狂屌你慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期六返10點早上 <br />\n冇門口入 卡係腦西到<br />\n個老閪可以三點半先返<br />\n結果我地坐係地下門口5個鐘<br />\n當佢返到嚟講咗句嘩你地咁舒服坐係地下wtf<br />\n真心向左走向右走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從來自己坐房intern自己出面做<br />\n但每十幾分鐘出嚟屌下你<br />\n侮辱你冇腦 手腳慢 進度差 <br />\n話咁樣出黎做5000蚊都比多你地<br />\nWtf最低工資都唔只啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我地intern可以一日幫佢做18個鐘先肯放你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要唔只一日 係日日起碼工作12個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個腦閪去法國三個星期吃喝玩樂<br />\n交低做野 問又唔應機做完又唔滿意<br />\n可以話乜憑咩拎返屋企做<br />\n今日比你地做應該要今日完<br />\n個時11半夜晚 有人住離島<br />\n我地心諗冇撚野啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果做完唔滿意唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然仲有好多 不過一定比大家知呢間<br />\n本土時裝品牌<br />\n'偽善下三流'<br />\n'當學生係狗'<br />\n'冇料扮四條'<br />\n'孤寒用到盡'<br />\n'侮辱屌冇腦'<br />\n嘅時裝品牌 - MODEMENT</blockquote>"},{"pid":"22d07fee10e1b2dcc3febae116829d794ea5590f","tid":345001,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"你地肯做係你地戇鳩，無你班戇鳩邊有得個老細咁惡?"},{"pid":"9e412b844d45a50e40156c7d605f1003b892b5d3","tid":345001,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"宜家讀緊咩？<br />\nIve? 1999咁款不如組織左先好講"},{"pid":"a6415d16fb2e014d8f8ae926b81ee408d09539a8","tid":345001,"uid":133092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地肯做係你地戇鳩，無你班戇鳩邊有得個老細咁惡?</blockquote><br />\n想當年覺得份實習報告重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91da7a08408775272cf2bc44758958555279a68","tid":345001,"uid":113866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"其實讀時裝有幾多出黎真係做返呢一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前返pt sales 9成同事都係讀設計，時裝呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 推"},{"pid":"5a7621ef6afd122f8f8e5f1f0672e3bd76999151","tid":345001,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家讀緊咩？<br />\nIve? 1999咁款不如組織左先好講</blockquote><br />\n段野係長左d 姐，何來1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"